  "steps": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a non-stick kadai, add dried coconut and sauté till golden brown.",
    "Add curry leaves and green chillies and mix well. Add onion. mix and sauté till golden brown.",
    "Add cumin powder, coriander powder, turmeric powder, garam masala powder, coarse red chilli powder and salt and mix well.",
    "Add chicken, mix and sauté on high heat for 2-3 minutes. Cook on medium heat for 8-10 minutes or till chicken is done.",
    "Transfer onto a serving plate, garnish with fried curry leaves and serve hot with Malabar parotta."
